## cleanUrlQueryString variable

Returns a URL with trailing "?" and "&amp;" characters removed.

e.g.:

- "/foo?" → "/foo" - "/foo?bar&amp;" → "/foo?bar"

**Signature:**

```typescript
cleanUrlQueryString: (url: string) => string
```
